<Body>
	<Title>广东湛江21名小学生疑因食用不洁食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008年2月21日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">南方都市报</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">2月21日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">信息</Denoter>：（记者 涂峰 通讯员 朱浩）</Event></Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">前日下午</Time>，<Location lid="l2">湛江市徐闻县下桥镇糖厂小学</Location>发生一起严重<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，<Event eid="e3">共有<Participant oid="o3">45名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d3" type="movement">送到</Denoter><Location lid="l3">医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event></Sentence>。<Sentence><Event eid="e5"><Time tid="t5" type="timeInterval">至目前止</Time>，确定<Denoter did="d5" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>的学生为<Participant sid="s5">21名</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e6">另<Participant sid="s6">24名入院学生</Participant>因精神过度<Denoter did="d6" type="perception">紧张</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e7">导致<Denoter did="d7" type="perception">肚痛</Denoter></Event>，现已排除食物中毒。</Sentence><Sentence>初步调查，<Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">学生</Participant>疑因<Denoter did="d9" type="action">食用</Denoter><Object oid="o8">不洁食物</Object></Event><Event eid="e9">引起<Denoter did="d9" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
     
　　<Paragraph><Sentence>据了解，<Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">2月19日11时许</Time>，徐闻县下桥镇糖厂小学的<Participant sid="s10">住校学生</Participant>在<Location lid="l10">饭堂里</Location><Denoter did="d10" type="action">吃</Denoter>过<Object oid="o10">中午饭</Object>后</Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">部分学生</Participant><Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>肚痛、呕吐或头晕等<Object oid="o11">中毒症状</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e12"><Time tid="t12" type="relTime">下午3时许</Time>，共有<Participant sid="s12">21名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d12" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter><Object did="d12">不适症状</Object></Event><Event eid="e13">并被紧急<Denoter did="d13" type="movement">送到</Denoter><Location lid="l13">下桥镇卫生院</Location></Event><Event eid="e14"><Denoter did="d14" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e15"><Time tid="t15" type="relTime">随后</Time>被<Denoter did="d15" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l15">徐闻县人民医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e16"><Denoter did="d16" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e17">据六年级学生<Participant sid="s17">宋文忠</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18">他</Participant>是因<Time tid="t18" type="relTime">中午</Time><Denoter did="d18" type="action">吃</Denoter>了<Object oid="o18">学校饭堂里的饭菜</Object>后</Event><Event eid="e19"><Denoter did="d19" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter><Object oid="o19">肚子疼痛</Object>的</Event>，<Event eid="e20">在旁边的<Participant sid="s20">两名女生</Participant>也<Denoter did="d21" type="action">点头</Denoter>表示</Event>，“<Event eid="e21"><Participant sid="s21">他们</Participant>都是<Denoter did="d21" type="action">吃</Denoter>了<Object oid="o21">中午饭</Object></Event>，感觉不舒服的。”</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e22">在医院治疗的<Participant sid="s22">学生</Participant>普遍<Denoter did="d22" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e23"><Participant sid="s23">他们</Participant><Time tid="t23" type="relTime">中午吃饭时</Time>都<Denoter did="d23" type="action">吃</Denoter>过<Object oid="o23">一种名叫雪豆的蔬菜</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e24"><Time tid="t24" type="relTime">当晚8点</Time>，<Participant sid="s24">医生</Participant><Denoter did="d24" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e25"><Participant sid="25s" type="recipient">21名学生</Participant>经<Denoter did="d25" type="operation">抢救</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e26">除了其中<Participant sid="s26">两名</Participant>仍有<Denoter did="d26" type="action">呕吐</Denoter>外</Event>，其余19名情况已稳定。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e27"><Participant sid="s27">徐闻县公安</Participant>、<Participant sid="s27">卫生</Participant>等部门已展开<Denoter did="d27" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>目前中毒原因仍不清楚，<Event eid="e28"><Participant sid="s28">有关部门</Participant>初步<Denoter did="d28" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e29"><Participant sid="s29">学生们</Participant>有可能因<Denoter did="d29" type="action">吃</Denoter>了<Object oid="o29">不洁雪豆</Object></Event>而<Event eid="e30">引起<Denoter did="d30" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
